{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}If you're a captain at all.

33
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:52,620
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Sergeant Evans, fetch the others.

34
