{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- Ah! Ow! - Another miracle.

38
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,850
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Miss Cathcart,you shouldn't do that.

39
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:13,640
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Cathcart. Florence Cathcart.

40
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:15,560
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}How dare you come here under false pretences?

