43
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:28,660
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Neither will your blood capsules which you slipped from your cup

44
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:32,160
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}and your handkerchief as we started.

45
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:36,370
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Nor your free hand pulling the wick from this woman's candle.

46
00:05:36,410 --> 00:05:39,250
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}As if the dead had something against naked flames.

47
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:42,340
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You're charlatans.

