{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Get them out of here, Evans.

50
00:05:51,220 --> 00:05:53,600
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Get off! You bastard.

51
