00:06:30,050 --> 00:06:33,640
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What, you don't want your colleagues seeing you bossed by a civilian woman?

56
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:37,310
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Uh, I mean, if anyone was going to order me around, it'd be...

57
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:40,480
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I mean, if Mrs Evans wasn't Mrs Evans...

58
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,730
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But she is.

59
00:06:41,810 --> 00:06:44,940
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}And she's very lucky, she is.

60
00:06:44,980 --> 00:06:47,650
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I won't bully you any more. Promise.

61
