00:08:38,550 --> 00:08:42,770
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Um, let him speak, Harry. Please.

77
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:47,440
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Um, I'm afraid Harry's right. I'm really not taking on any more work.

