{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But you are a ghost hunter as well as an author?

79
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,780
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Well, you can't hunt what doesn't exist.

