00:08:55,610 --> 00:08:57,610
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Ah, well, that's just it.

81
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:01,620
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We think we have one that does.

82
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,960
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I need to change.

83
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:11,130
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Katie, will you show Mr Mallory to my study.

84
00:09:11,250 --> 00:09:13,300
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- Yes, miss. - I'll be fine.

