{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Well, all memories are a hoax of some sort.

809
01:33:30,520 --> 01:33:33,390
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You can't blame anyone for letting you believe that one.

810
01:33:34,350 --> 01:33:35,900
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Mmm.

811
01:33:41,110 --> 01:33:42,530
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You needn't worry.

812
01:33:44,780 --> 01:33:46,740
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No one will find Judd's body.

813
01:33:49,740 --> 01:33:52,160
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I've buried better men than him.

814
01:33:56,040 --> 01:33:58,250
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You see your own ghosts, too?

815
01:34:06,760 --> 01:34:10,350
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Are they with us now?

816
