{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}They look like my friends.

818
01:34:28,620 --> 01:34:30,950
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}They don't have the right.

819
01:34:31,410 --> 01:34:34,580
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No amount of guilt deserves the pain you inflict on yourself.

