{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}isn't a life at all.

823
01:34:45,340 --> 01:34:46,630
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We may as well

