{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But it's all right now.

836
01:36:10,970 --> 01:36:12,840
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Because he can have you forever.

837
01:36:13,510 --> 01:36:15,010
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Everything in its place.

838
01:36:17,100 --> 01:36:18,520
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Maud

