841
01:36:27,190 --> 01:36:28,610
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Florence?

842
01:36:30,110 --> 01:36:32,780
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- Florence? - Mr Mallory!-

843
01:36:33,620 --> 01:36:36,620
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Florence and I will be leaving now.

