01:36:40,500 --> 01:36:42,540
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Florence? Florence?

846
01:36:43,250 --> 01:36:46,590
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Robert, the medicine cabinet in Maud's room. Quickly.

847
01:36:46,960 --> 01:36:49,460
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Something to make me sick. Something to make me sick.

848
01:36:49,550 --> 01:36:52,630
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Oh, God! No! No!

849
01:36:56,890 --> 01:37:02,230
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Tom?

850
01:37:05,400 --> 01:37:09,940
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Don't be angry, I just miss you.

851
01:37:10,400 --> 01:37:12,240
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}All the time.

852
01:37:14,660 --> 01:37:18,240
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}My whole life I've never been happy, not one second since you left me.

853
01:37:19,120 --> 01:37:23,500
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But I can't... I can't... I can't come.

854
01:37:24,000 --> 01:37:25,420
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You know that, don't you?

855
01:37:28,210 --> 01:37:30,260
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You're the only friend I've ever had.

856
01:37:32,720 --> 01:37:36,300
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But if I go with you now, my soul will never be happy, and I...

