01:37:37,600 --> 01:37:40,010
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I can be, thanks to you.

858
01:37:41,060 --> 01:37:42,640
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But you won't need me.

859
01:37:43,100 --> 01:37:45,100
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No one will need me.

860
01:37:46,360 --> 01:37:48,690
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Tom, you must be brave.

861
