{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Are you dying?

868
01:38:28,650 --> 01:38:30,060
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I don't know.

