01:38:41,080 --> 01:38:42,490
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I promise.

873
01:38:43,700 --> 01:38:45,750
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Even if you can't see me.

874
01:38:48,630 --> 01:38:50,040
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I can...

875
01:38:50,540 --> 01:38:53,050
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I can feel you now.

876
01:39:51,400 --> 01:39:53,820
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'll tell the boys it was an accident, of course.

